title: Seven Soldiers of Victory
description:
The complete Seven Soldiers of Victory; follows the individual adventures of the team that is not a team, working towards different ends that cumulatively saves the world. Every member of the team remains unaware of the others existence.

Prologue material includes the JLA Ultramarines storyline as well as their final fate in JLA Classified, which introduces Nebuloh the Huntsman and the Sheeda (the nemeses of the Seven Soldiers).

All credit to the original editors of this all digital collection and the one who helped make the prologue material complete with JLA Classified 1-3.
